title: Chuck Wicks - Starting Now
description:
This is what great country is all about...great songs sung by a great singer! I had heard "Stealing Cinderella" and was impressed, so when I saw the full length CD I was curious enough to sample it. I am glad I did. Every song here is strong enough to be played on today&#039;s contemporary country radio. This is the kind of CD that is worth purchasing instead of just downloading a few songs. It is actually a great listen from beginning to end. If you&#039;re a country fan, do yourself a favor and buy this now! Sounds like this artist should be around for quite a while.
